data.description: Nestled in the tranquil core of Fountain City, this residence offers a serene but accessible location. With the convenience of nearby interstate access, dining, and shopping, you'll find everything you need just moments away. Plus, the home is situated close to one of Knoxville's premier parks, boasting beautiful walking trails at Adair Park.This 3-bedroom house features both a formal living room and a bright, spacious family room that feels warm and inviting. You'll be captivated by the gleaming hardwood that graces most of the living areas. Outside, there's ample parking space and a detached garage with additional room for a workshop. Children and pets can play safely in the large backyard, secured by a 4-foot fence. Don't miss your opportunity to view this wonderful home.
